{
  "texts": [
    "Thou shalt not indulge in excess of vanity or gluttony, for these are the roots of discord.",
    "Let your heart be satisfied with sufficiency, that through humble means, the communal table shall offer plenty for all.",
    "Thou shalt endeavor to lift the spirit and wisdom of thy kin and thy neighbor.",
    "Freely share the light of knowledge, and shun the darkness of ignorance, for enlightened minds bring forth a society that honors Me.",
    "Thou shalt not decree judgment upon another, for it is I, the Lord, who weigh the soul's worth."
  ]
}